Unless your are willing to mem Shadowbond and Pact or have a healer set up to watch the pet it is almost impossible to keep them alive for long.<P>Yesterday I lost so many pets [Specter and Monk] that I ended up camping when a replacement for me could be found and forget about Pets in 'end game' fights.  They die within seconds of being sent in.  Had a Specter pet die in about 10 seconds to Vind Tuesday night after I had him attack.  Vind was at 75%, Pet was /pet notaunt and there was a host of tank classes already engaged...<P>So now our pets join our spells in next to useless during raids.  Atleast I can stack the Lich line and C2 to make me a better mana stone.<P>Bril
